name: Without Blinking
description: Surrealistrasyon//Şerif Gümüşbaş//Mixed Technique//3500x4500 pixel//Watch life without blinking to see it until the last moment. Watch the era you live in, the history and the future too. feel the chaos inside and go on living feeling like you don't know anything//Drawing is an impressive language for me with its universal and differentiating structure in every viewer. I also love and use the automatism method because it is a pleasant and mysterious way to express myself and what I perceive about existence, the world, and life.
